OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774569807
OL,3,CPharmacy staff reveal extent of
OL,4,C'escalating' abuse from patients
OL,6,F"People will come in and really be
OL,7,Fintimidating with our over the counter
OL,8,Fstaff when they're not getting the
OL,9,Fresult that they intended," says
OL,10,FNishaan Sanjay, the owner of a Fareham-
OL,11,Fbased pharmacy.
OL,13,FHis experience mirrors those found
OL,14,Facross the industry in England, after
OL,15,Fa nationwide survey uncovered a
OL,16,Fworrying trend of "escalating abuse"
OL,17,Ffrom patients towards pharmacy staff.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
